Company Overview of Evermore Funds Trust - Evermore Global Value Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Evermore Funds Trust - Evermore Global Value Fund is an open ended balanced mutual fund launched and managed by Evermore Global Advisors, LLC. It invests in public equity and fixed income markets of countries across the globe. For its equity portion, the fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in value stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations. For its fixed income portion, the fund primarily invests in bank debt, lower-rated or defaulted debt securities, comparable unrated debt securities, or other indebtedness companies which are of any rating and maturity. It employs fundamental analysis focusing on facto...
Evermore Funds Trust - Evermore Global Value Fund is an open ended balanced mutual fund launched and managed by Evermore Global Advisors, LLC. It invests in public equity and fixed income markets of countries across the globe. For its equity portion, the fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in value stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations. For its fixed income portion, the fund primarily invests in bank debt, lower-rated or defaulted debt securities, comparable unrated debt securities, or other indebtedness companies which are of any rating and maturity. It employs fundamental analysis focusing on factors such as market price of a company’s securities, analysis of book value, cash flow potential, long-term earnings, and multiples of earnings, management changes, shareholder activism, and operational and financial restructurings, and strength of the management teams to create its portfolio. The fund seeks to benchmark the performance of its portfolio against the MSCI All-Country World Index (USD), the MSCI All-Country World Index Ex USA (USD), and the HFRX Event Driven Index. Evermore Funds Trust - Evermore Global Value Fund was formed on January 1, 2010 and is domiciled in the United States.
